---
// About section with grid layout and image with green tint overlay
---

<section id="about" class="max-w-[1000px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-12 py-24">
  <!-- Section Heading -->
  <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-lightest-slate font-mono whitespace-nowrap">
      <span class="text-green">01.</span> About Me
    </h2>
    <div class="h-[1px] bg-lightest-navy w-full max-w-xs"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Grid Layout: Text Left, Image Right -->
  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[2fr_1fr] gap-12 items-start">
    <!-- Text Content -->
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed">
        My journey started with a deep curiosity about how products come to life and solve real-world problems. Today, I'm focused on executing at the intersection of process architecture and cloud automation.
      </p>
      
      <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed">
        I believe that the best solutions don't just live in slide decks—they are tested in production. That's why I've hands-on developed a scalable toolkit that bridges frontend frameworks like Astro with robust backend orchestrations.
      </p>

      <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Here is a breakdown of my current skill set and infrastructure toolkit:
      </p>

      <!-- Tech Stack Matrix -->
      <div class="space-y-6 mt-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-green font-mono text-[13px] mb-3 uppercase tracking-widest">Strategic</h3>
          <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-sm">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate font-mono"><span class="text-green">▹</span> Process Mapping</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate font-mono"><span class="text-green">▹</span> Product Lifecycle</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate font-mono"><span class="text-green">▹</span> Business Value Discovery</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-green font-mono text-[13px] mb-3 uppercase tracking-widest">Technical</h3>
          <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-sm">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate font-mono"><span class="text-green">▹</span> Python</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate font-mono"><span class="text-green">▹</span> SQL</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate font-mono"><span class="text-green">▹</span> Astro</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate font-mono"><span class="text-green">▹</span> RAG Architecture</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-green font-mono text-[13px] mb-3 uppercase tracking-widest">Data & Insights</h3>
          <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-sm">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate font-mono"><span class="text-green">▹</span> Tableau</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate font-mono"><span class="text-green">▹</span> NeonDB (Cloud Storage)</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate font-mono"><span class="text-green">▹</span> Vector Databases</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Infrastructure & Tools -->
      <div class="mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-lightest-navy/50">
        <h3 class="text-green font-mono text-[13px] mb-3 uppercase tracking-widest">Infrastructure &amp; Tools</h3>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-6 gap-y-3 font-mono text-xs text-slate-400">
          <span class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-600"></span> <span>Google Cloud</span></span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-600"></span> <span>n8n</span></span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-600"></span> <span>NeonDB</span></span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-600"></span> <span>Render</span></span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-600"></span> <span>Antigravity</span></span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Image with Green Tint Overlay -->
    <div class="relative group max-w-[300px] mx-auto md:mx-0">
      <!-- Border that shifts on hover -->
      <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-full h-full border-2 border-green rounded group-hover:bottom-0 group-hover:right-0 transition-all duration-300 z-0"></div>
      
      <!-- Image Container -->
      <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded z-10">
        <img 
          src="/me.jpeg" 
          alt="Vashisth Patel"
          class="relative z-10 rounded grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-300"
        />
        <!-- Green Tint Overlay that fades on hover -->
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-green/40 mix-blend-multiply group-hover:bg-transparent transition-all duration-300 z-20"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
